{
  "key": 50102,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainOutside_Text_LetsDoThis",
      "en_US": [
        "Grunt 1: This is it!\n",
        "Stark Mountain!\r",
        "Now we need to get deep inside.\n",
        "Let’s do this!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainOutside_Text_CanHeReplaceCyrus",
      "en_US": [
        "Grunt 2: Yeah, but...\n",
        "All this just for a bit of heat?\r",
        "Aren’t the Veilstone generators\n",
        "enough for Master Cyrus?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainOutside_Text_GoodTimeToBeDone",
      "en_US": [
        "Grunt 1: Not even close.\r",
        "Commander Charon says this mountain\n",
        "burns hotter than anytthing we built.\r",
        "Master Cyrus needs that power... and\n",
        "I’m not about to tell him no."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainOutside_Text_InhaledVolcanicAsh",
      "en_US": [
        "Looker: Whew! The air outside, it is\n",
        "delicious, yes!\r",
        "...Gweh! Gah! Geff! Bleah!\r",
        "I have inhaled the volcanic ash by\n",
        "the lungful!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainOutside_Text_MagmaStone",
      "en_US": [
        "Now, you two.\n",
        "This is what they were after.\r",
        "The Magma Stone.\r",
        "Moving this is said to awaken the\n",
        "Pokémon HEATRAN.\r",
        "The old tales say that its awakening,\n",
        "it will make Stark Mountain erupt.\r",
        "...But I have moved it. It is here.\n",
        "Will this cause the eruption?!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainOutside_Text_IllPutItBack",
      "en_US": [
        "Buck: Hey, don’t sweat it, stranger.\r",
        "Give me that Magma Stone.\n",
        "I’ll go put it back for you.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainOutside_Text_WorkIsFinished",
      "en_US": [
        "Looker: That boy, he has quite the\n",
        "energy, yes?\r",
        "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}, I should tell you why\n",
        "I have arrived here.\r",
        "After we parted at the Mt. Coronet,\n",
        "I investigated their hideout.\r",
        "I uncovered Charon’s plot, which led\n",
        "me to a stakeout of this place.\r",
        "That Charon is now securely within our\n",
        "custody.\r",
        "It is safe to say the Team Galactic is\n",
        "a threat no longer.\r",
        "That being said, it looks like my work\n",
        "here is finally finished.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainOutside_Text_SwingByMyPlace",
      "en_US": [
        "Buck: Hey, stranger!\n",
        "I put the Magma Stone where it belongs.\r",
        "It’ll be OK now.\n",
        "HEATRAN won’t wake up. Probably.\r",
        "But, hey, {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}!\n",
        "You’re an amazing Trainer!\r",
        "Swing by my place later.\n",
        "It’s in the Survival Area.\r",
        "Be seeing you, stranger, {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}!\n",
        "Bye-bye!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainOutside_Text_FarewellMyFriend",
      "en_US": [
        "Buck: Hey.\n",
        "Everything may not have gone our way.\r",
        "But I want to thank you for helping\n",
        "rid this place of Team Galactic.\r",
        "Being able to use the power of the\n",
        "mountain, HEATRAN...\r",
        "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}, you need to put a\n",
        "stop to whatever they’re planning.\r",
        "Don’t count me out though! The Magma\n",
        "Stone is sacred, and I’ll stop at\f",
        "nothing to return it here and restore\f",
        "Stark Mountain to how it should be.\r",
        "I’m sure we’ll meet again\n",
        "soon, {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainOutside_Text_SignStarkMountain",
      "en_US": [
        "Stark Mountain\n",
        "Eruption Zone!"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
